				<>
					<div class="terms-block">
						<h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
						<p>
							By using Rayo Consulting services, you fully accept these Terms of Service. 
							If you do not accept these terms, do not use our services.
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="terms-block">
						<h2>2. Who We Are</h2>
						<div class="company-info">
							<p>
								<strong>Rayo Consulting</strong> is a company specialized in web development, mobile applications, and AI solutions, 
